    "source": {
      "goCharacterKey": "Razor",
      "note": "Generated from Genshin Optimizer sheets (master) + allStat_gen skillParam. Hit keys match GO target paths; multKey = <hitKey>_mult. Levels: Lv10, except constellation-boosted talents of 4-star characters at Lv13 (C6 assumed). Normal/charged/plunging default to physical unless the sheet overrides the element (infusions are NOT applied). burst.companionDmg1-4 (Wolf's Bite lightning strikes proc'd on Normal Attack hits 1-4) manually derived from GO's actual sheet formula (libs/gi/sheets/src/Characters/Razor/index.tsx): companionDmg{n}_mult = normal.{n}_mult (Lv10) x burst companionDmg scalar (skillParam_gen.burst[1], Lv13 = 0.51); the formula/data.ts stub for Razor is an unmigrated placeholder and was not the source. constellation6.dmg (Lupus Fulguris lightning strike) = flat 100% ATK Electro DMG (GO: `prod(percent(dm.constellation6.dmg), input.total.atk)`, dm.constellation6.dmg = 1), untagged by any normal/skill/burst dmgBonusKey per GO's customDmgNode('elemental', ...) categorization — only electro_dmg_/all_dmg_ apply. lockedPassive.dmg (v6.2 Hexerei: Secret Rite AoE lightning strike, requires 2+ Hexerei party members + Witch's Homework: Of the Little Wolf Pack) = flat 150% ATK Electro DMG (GO: `skillParam_gen.lockedPassive[1][0]` = 1.5, gated `tally.hexerei>=2` + `condLockHomework`), same untagged 'elemental' categorization as C6. The companion Wolf Within +70% ATK flat DMG bonus (`skillParam_gen.lockedPassive[0][0]` = 0.7, GO's `lock_burst_dmgInc`) is passed ONLY into companionDmg1-4's `premod.burst_dmgInc` (NOT into burst.dmg) — modeled via each companionDmg hit's `flatDmgIncFromAtkRatioKeys: [\"razorWolfWithinDmgIncFromAtk_\"]` plus the buffs.self_conditional_modifiers_json `hexereiWolfWithinDmgInc` entry, so it never leaks onto Razor's own Lightning Fang hit. Energy restore (7) and the 1s internal cooldown on the AoE strike are not modeled (no dmg-formula effect).",
      "assumptions": {
        "constellation": 6,
        "characterLevel": 90,
        "autoTalentLevel": 10,
        "skillTalentLevel": 13,
        "burstTalentLevel": 13
      }
    }
  },
